{"tid":1029251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【向鹹網宣戰】孟加拉禁2萬色情網 政府：這是場持久戰","createTime":"2019-02-20T06:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T10:20:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e52e107ca3517ad9caf8b33d363751cf8fe9e90c","tid":1029251,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190220/large/1550634886_18be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190220%2Flarge%2F1550634886_18be.jpg&h=08e935b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n孟加拉展開反色情網站行動，周二封鎖近2萬個網站，互聯網服務供應商在電訊監管機構要求下，過去一周已封鎖了大量色情及賭博網站。<br />\n相關新聞：【不滿藝人太似樣】想限制女團「靚女不可過多」 南韓當局被轟似獨裁<br />\n<br />\n郵政及電訊部長賈巴爾（Mustafa Jabbar）表示：「我希望為所有孟加拉人打造一個安全的互聯網環境，這是向色情影片宣戰，而且會是場持久戰。」<br />\n大部份遭封鎖的網站都外國網站，但少數當地網站及社交平台也受打擊，包括大受歡迎的社交app「抖音」及「Bigo」。警方周日更譴責一位人氣急升的女演員，要求她刪除在Facebook、Instagram和抖音上的暴露照片及影片。<br />\n相關新聞：【向鹹網宣戰】色情業經濟效益不容忽視 以美國計年賺至少$390億<br />\n<br />\n賈巴爾強調當局正監視fb專頁、Youtube頻道及網頁等，「其中有部份因含淫褻內容已被封鎖，我們建議其他人不要發佈違反社會規範的內容」。<br />\n孟加拉人口達1.65億，有逾9,000萬人是互聯網用戶，色情片女星的名字經常性出現在熱門搜尋內容上。當地民風保守，大部份人信奉伊斯蘭教，高等法院去年接到民事組織投訴，指大量成人網站含有未經審查及淫穢內容。法院11月要求政府以半年為限，禁絕色情網站及以電子形式出版的淫褻物品。<br />\n當地互聯網服務供應商協會秘書長霍克（Emdadul Hoque）表示，他們已遵守命令，但不少用戶仍可透過虛擬私人網絡（VPN）等方法連接色情網站。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"5eacd93f951f3cf052b412f0f9b6d6822be2e0ab","tid":1029251,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190220/59280635?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F59280635%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8wNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=b8cb3024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190220%2F59280635%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_web%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&h=0b4e440e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190220/59280635?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_web&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2</a>"},{"pid":"3e286c3d7c847f9b30d40dcb13277b2eab23fac6","tid":1029251,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec4cb432fbdc30287799dd3c7d10e9ef8cdd9482","tid":1029251,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"黑皮膚叫黑人 白皮膚叫白人 佢地係咪叫泥人"},{"pid":"20d175607b1578f1dbe753ff6699978e87c9aa67","tid":1029251,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:13:39.000Z","msg":"靠諗力打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc36f4af3a020cab01638354550283a26c4f30e2","tid":1029251,"uid":56223,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:13:51.000Z","msg":"連登幾年前已經自發做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩網擺出來一齊block"},{"pid":"bfb9f47a1aa3544d14351d80a48726495a44d95a","tid":1029251,"uid":5715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"唔比打J唯有叫雞，又促進經濟發展<br />\n唔比打J，去老強，又推高警察就業率"},{"pid":"99ef760be5d7de770b980170bf8b953b52ac6f9e","tid":1029251,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9c1bcf263ebc7db849b7ca9de82e0e01ce1553","tid":1029251,"uid":161063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec4cb432fbdc30287799dd3c7d10e9ef8cdd9482","tid":1029251